{"tid":558584,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[MHW] monhunt.com 又加多咗新功能啦","createTime":"2018-02-12T11:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T13:41:00.000Z","uid":119163,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8021ba3d39dc4135932c8ad50760a200bf2f8da5","tid":558584,"uid":119163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"https://monhunt.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmonhunt.com%2F&d=NpnKHSwCX8BEIioKffU0HwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=54bc0d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://monhunt.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n上一個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/551094/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/551094/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n首先好多謝大家嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n上次個網出完之後，收到唔少熱心巴打嘅意見，<br />\n我呢幾日都趕工更新個網，加多左交友功能，始終即時約戰係有點限制。<br />\n<br />\n目前新增咗嘅功能如下：<br />\n<br />\nA. 即時約戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n無論係開場，更新約戰都會實時反映係用家嘅約戰列表上<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1kr0f7wo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1kr0f7wo&h=b63344c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nB. 長期約戰/交友區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <br />\n大家可以留自己PSN喺度等人加，可以係備註講下自己幾時online或者想刷咩任/龍多<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qgckfx93\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqgckfx93&h=51a6ea8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC. 即時聊天室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <br />\n等大家可以係等人嘅時候可以搵人吹下水，新手又可以問野，老手又可以幫下新手或者吹下水<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/741olcx0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F741olcx0&h=5fd11067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n即時約戰用法:<br />\n1.先係game開場<br />\n2.上 <a href=\"https://monhunt.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmonhunt.com%2F&d=NpnKHSwCX8BEIioKffU0HwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=54bc0d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://monhunt.com/</a> &gt; 即時約戰 &gt; 按「募集」<br />\n3.輸入相關資料<br />\n4.等人入<br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n成功配對後，需要手動將狀態設定為已開始，以免其他人繼續撞，多謝合作<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有咩意見可以係度講返，thanks! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006913c1f9805af41fc69cdf37bbbd23f77f4609","tid":558584,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"巴打真係好有心<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"71c9fb81b4cce4f8817cdddb4522bdd4bcd03589","tid":558584,"uid":119163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"006913c1f9805af41fc69cdf37bbbd23f77f4609","tid":558584,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"巴打真係好有心<br />\n幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400660a9ed07a3a696a4d16443e6b89737f34957","tid":558584,"uid":119163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3477dc804e25e0903fa7977fb5b38a44bb26cda1","tid":558584,"uid":63918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63628a069d551cdecd71a61cd62a1ea54d66855","tid":558584,"uid":119163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3477dc804e25e0903fa7977fb5b38a44bb26cda1","tid":558584,"uid":63918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal